entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You helped Stregand copy a rival corporate labs bio-engineering.
entries.journal_entry_description: Stregand owns a rival corporate lab, and he is willing to pay you to gather blood samples from the engineered creatures of a nearby lab. Go to the lab and collect the blood samples.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Stregand wants you to get him some samples of blood from the Engineered Creatures. He is going to use them to copy the process for his own corporation.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Gather Samples of Engineered Creatures' Blood
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Ah yes, I am receiving the chemical compositions of the blood samples now. Good work. This should be enough to put them out of business. Your payment is being transferred now.
